Package: nonneg.cg
Type: Package
Title: Non-Negative CG Minimizer
Version: 0.1
Date: 2019-01-03
Author: David Cortes
Maintainer: David Cortes <david.cortes.rivera@gmail.com>
Description: Minimize a differentiable function subject to all the variables being non-negative (i.e. >= 0),
  using a Conjugate-Gradient algorithm based on the Polak-Rubiere-Polyak formula.
